''l mnogi mostovi pasti

00:56:45.059 --> 00:56:47.478
''l kipovi velikana

00:56:47.561 --> 00:56:50.397
''Nestat će

00:56:51.982 --> 00:56:54.151
''A najstariji simbol Londona

00:56:56.111 --> 00:56:58.447
''Ostat će uvijek isti.''

